stonishing history of the 19th century in Europe from Spain to Russia.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aEuropexHistory. 0aMonarchyzEuropexHistoryy19th century. 0aMonarchyzEuropexHistoryy20th century. 0aRestorations, Political. 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA History 2000 - 2014z9783110635836oZDB-23-GHI08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Complete Package 2014z9783110369526oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2014z9783110370225oZDB-23-DEG0 cEPUBz97831103707990 cprintz978348676504540uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978311035437940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110354379423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110354379/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEGb2014  aZDB-23-DGGb2014  aZDB-23-GHIc2000d2014